## 📐 Key DAX Measures

```dax
-- Example measure
Total Sales = SUM(fact_sales[SalesAmount])

-- YTD Sales
Sales YTD = TOTALYTD([Total Sales], dim_date[Date])
``` Avg Performance
Avg Performance = AVERAGE(HRDataset_v14[PerfScoreID])
--- Active Headcount Monthly
Active Headcount Monthly = 
CALCULATE(
    COUNTROWS(HRDataset_v14),
    HRDataset_v14[DateofHire] <= MAX(Calendar[Date]),
    OR(
        ISBLANK(HRDataset_v14[DateofTermination]),
        HRDataset_v14[DateofTermination] > MAX(Calendar[Date])
    )
)

--- Growth Headcount Rate 
Growth Headcount Rate % = DIVIDE([Active Headcount Monthly]-[Previous Period], [Previous Period],  "BLANK")



